        <td bgcolor='black' valign=top width='100' nowrap><font color='white' face='Verdana' size='2'><b>Velous</b></font></td>
        <td bgcolor='black' valign='top' width='100%'><font color='white' face='Verdana' size='2'> I have been very busy lately. Between finding a job, getting ready for college, and other things, I have had little time to write about our hero (deviant?) necromancer. However; for you fans out there, I will let you know that I am still into my project. Here is a section from what I have written.</P><P>"It is time," I heard some old grey voice echoing around me like thunder. I was then placed in shackles and their icy fine steel death grip hurt my wrists and ankles like hell. I almost choked as a cold goblet was thrust at my mouth pouring some vile burning acidic liquid down my throat. Whatever it was, it burnt my insides with an unquenchable black fire as it went to my stomach and the rest of my body. I felt myself going numb as the sickness came over me. My arms and legs became as heavy as the marble pillars that supported the Great Library of Neriak. I began to fall towards the abyss as I lost my balance. I could feel the unnatrual strength of my bindings as they held me partialy upright. Then the darkness started to devour me as I heard someone scream.</P><P>The black hole of blinding darkness drew closer as I fell into it at a lightning speed that would make any bard envious. Then my universe was shattered by this pain that just seemed to become me. It enveloped me and held onto my soul like an unholy leach draining my sanity dry. I felt comforted by the Darkness, the Pain... then there was nothing. No gods, no paradise, no altered plains of existance, just an empty void with me in it...</P><P>I hope that you have patience with me as I continue this story of great darkness. This part of the story is nothing but bones for now (no pun intended) but I will "flesh" it out as I have time.</P><P>always thinking...(proccessing)...<BR>Velous</P><P>"I don't talk to dead people; I make them scream."</P><P>"I make dead people."</font></td>
